title: Mont. County Sheriff's Office EMC blotter
title_page: Mont. County Sheriff's Office EMC blotter
maintext:
On Nov. 23, Deputy Cooke was dispatched to East Martin Drive, in regards to a disturbance. After arriving on scene, a 15-year-old male was arrested for assault and evading.
On Nov. 23, Deputy Gallagher was patrolling the area of Pickering Road and observed a suspicious person walking down the road. After making contact the 22-year-old female, she was arrested for two counts of possession of a controlled substance.
On Nov. 27, Deputy White was dispatched to Pickering Road, in regards to a disturbance in progress. After arriving on scene, a 24-year-old male was arrested for aggravated assault with a deadly weapon.
